Circle: B
Cross: A
Triangle: Y
Square: X

operator:
x = go to backdrop (deposit)
o = retract deposit
left trigger = cycle counterclockwise on wrist
right trigger = cycle clockwise on wrist
left bumper = toggle left claw
right bumper = toggle right claw
press down on right joystick = open both claws
press down on left joystick = close both claws

dpad up = increase pixel backdrop slides height
dpad down = decrease pixel backdrop slide height
dpad left =
dpad right =
left joystick = manual control for deposit slides (up = increase, down = decrease)
right joystick =
